# The Purr

The most efficient mammalian sound.

<!-- pause -->

- Frequency: **25вҖ“150 Hz**
<!-- pause -->
- Same range used in **bone-density therapy** for human astronauts
<!-- pause -->
- A purring cat is, technically, **medical equipment**

<!-- note: This always gets a reaction. Pause after "medical equipment" for at least two full seconds. -->
