# Hunting Prowess

How cats stack up against the rest of the predator world.

| Predator        | Success Rate | Notes                          |
|-----------------|--------------|--------------------------------|
| Lion            | ~25%         | Group hunters                  |
| Wolf            | ~14%         | Stamina pursuit                |
| Polar bear      | ~10%         | Cold and patient               |
| **House cat**   | **~32%**     | **Highest of all listed**      |
| Great white     | ~50%         | (asterisks: ambush specialist) |

<!-- note: The house cat number surprises everyone. Lean into it вҖ” this is the "wait, what?" moment of the talk. -->
