# Adopt, Don't Shop

Three things to do this week.

- **Visit your local shelter.** Even if you don't adopt вҖ” the cats benefit from socialization.
<!-- pause -->
- **Sponsor a senior cat.** Older cats are the hardest to place and the easiest to live with.
<!-- pause -->
- **Tell one person about TNR programs.** Trap-neuter-return is the single most effective cat welfare intervention in the world.

<!-- note: End slow. Let the room sit with this one. Don't rush to "thank you." -->
